 website which was was just one static page with a list of my projects. At the time I made it that was enough, but I wanted to extend it at some point to be a place where I can do and show more things, not necessarily related to web development. I guess this is that point.","featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.8181818181818181,"src":"/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/2f1b1/header.jpg","srcSet":"/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/fd013/header.jpg 200w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/25252/header.jpg 400w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/2f1b1/header.jpg 800w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/0ff54/header.jpg 1200w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/06655/header.jpg 1600w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/7cb48/header.jpg 4426w","srcWebp":"/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/ccdb5/header.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/6b183/header.webp 200w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/fc32b/header.webp 400w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/ccdb5/header.webp 800w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/9000d/header.webp 1200w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/e0075/header.webp 1600w,\n/static/11a5d35ab3f48dbb5eb86082112e16be/5275b/header.webp 4426w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"tag":"web"}}}